<p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://manual.audacityteam.org/o/man/audacity_tracks_and_clips.html">This manual page</a> describes how Audacity uses the terms "tracks" and "clips", and how to "split" (cut or delete), merge, and time-shift clips.</p>
